          "scid": "thig1.18:1.0.3",
          "en": "18. Saṃghā"
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig1.18:1.0.4",
          "en": "“Home have I left, for I have left my world! Child have I left, and all my cherish’d herds! Lust have I left, and Ill-will, too, is gone, And Ignorance have I put far from me; Craving and root of Craving overpowered, Cool am I now, knowing Nibbana’s peace.”"
        }
